metadata.name: Tic-tac-toe
metadata.description:
[Must read] Introducing the Blacktober series with "Tic-tac-toe," a piece inspired by Morticia and Gomez Adams's love story. 

What is Blacktober? It is an art challenge for Black artists to showcase their skill whether it was to share OCâ€™s, cosplay as their favorite characters, draw their favorite Black characters, or (the most popular form of participation) reimagining popular characters from cartoons, movies, and more as Black or Black mixed.
